text: Krasnyye Gorki () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Toykinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 18 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 3 km east from Toykino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Krasnyye Gorki
